document_data.[[Eye on the Realms]]: The Gentle Ghost:
: ''By [[Ed Greenwood]], illustrated by [[Matias Tapia]].'' '''p. 85-87'''
Wherever in the Realms you find battlefields, fortresses, or long-established settlements, you will also find hauntings. One such that has risen to popular notice only recently is a spectral, flying lady [[elf]] who has become known as "the Gentle Ghost of [[Silverymoon]]" for her kindly manner. {{Dusup|175/Eye on the Realms: The Gentle Ghost of Silverymoon}}
